<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Form</title>
    
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Baloo';
            src: url('https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/balootamma2/v2/vEFK2_hCAgcR46PaajtrYlBbd7wf8tK1W77HtMo.ttf') format('truetype');
        }

        /* Set page size to A4, portrait */
        @page {
            size: A4 portrait;
            margin: 12mm;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Baloo', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
            margin: 0;
            /*width: 210mm;*/
            width: 300mm;
            height: 297mm;
            
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        .header-table {
            width: 100%;
            border: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .header-table td {
            vertical-align: top;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
        }

        .header-text {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header-text h1, .header-text h2, .header-text p, .header-text h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header-text h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header-text h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .header-text p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .header-text h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .photo-box {
            width: 160px;
            height: 180px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .photo-box p {
            font-size: 10px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .form-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .signature {
            border-top: 1px solid black;
            width: 200px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
 
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        /* Styling for lines above and below the content */
        .line-section {
            border-top: 1px solid black;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin: 0px 0;
        }

        .line-section p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .separator {
          border-bottom: 1px solid black; /* Creates a horizontal line */
          margin: 10px 0; /* Adjust spacing */
        }
        
        .table-bordered th, .table-bordered td {
           border-left: 0px;
           border-top: 0px;
           border-bottom: 0px;
           border-right: 1px solid black !important;
           border-collapse: collapse !important;
           font-weight: normal;
        }

        .table-bordered{width: 100%}
        .table-bordered   th:first-child, .table-bordered   td:first-child, .table-bordered   td.left-align, .table-bordered.left-align td, .table.left-align td{text-align: left; padding-left: 0px}
        .table-bordered   th:last-child{border-right: 0px !important}
        .table-bordered   td:last-child{border-right: 0px !important}
        .table-bordered td.with-border{border-bottom: 1px solid black !important;}
        .table.without-border td{border-bottom: 0px !important;}
        
        .table.zero-margin{margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px}
        .small-padding th, .small-padding td {padding: 5px 10px}
        div.no-margin{margin: 0px}
        
        
        th, td {
          padding: 6px;
          text-align: center;
        }
        
         .box {
            border: 2px solid black;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .signatures {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .office-note {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
}

   .left {
      float: left;
      text-align: left;
    }

.right {
    float: right;
    width: 50%;
}

 .clearfix {
      clear:both;
    }
        .right-align {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .align-center {
          text-align: center;
        }
        
       .labels {
      display: flex;
      display: -webkit-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      white-space: nowrap; /* Prevents label text wrapping */
      
    }

    .value {
       
      padding: 5px;
      margin-left: 20px;
      min-width: 200px; /* Ensures space for name */
    }

    
    .wrapper {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; /* Left column auto-size, right column flexible */
      gap: 10px; /* Space between columns */
      align-items: center; /* Centers "Vijendra Rao" vertically */
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .table-layout {
  display: table;
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
}

.table-row {
  display: table-row;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
}

.table-row.no-border{
    border-bottom: none;
}

.table-cell {
  display: table-cell;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  vertical-align: top; /* Ensures text aligns properly */
}

.table-row .table-cell:first-child{
  padding: 5px 0px; 
}

.number {
  width: 1%; /* Adjust width as needed */
  text-align: left; /* Aligns numbers to the right */
  font-weight: bold;
}

.labels {
  width: 30%; /* Adjust width as needed */
}

.labels .label-text {
  display: block; /* Each label appears on a new line */
}

.value {
  width: 35%;
  padding-left: 20px; /* Adds space between labels and value */
  white-space: nowrap; /* Ensures the value doesn’t wrap */
  vertical-align: middle;
}

 .page, .page-break { clear: both; page-break-after: always; }
 

       .table-bordered th.number{border-right: 0px !important; vertical-align: top}
       .table-bordered thead th.left-align{text-align: left}
       .table-bordered tr td.no-border{border-right: 0 !important; border-left: 0 !important; }
    </style>

 
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <!-- Header Section as a Table -->
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <!-- Left-aligned Logo -->
            <td style="width: 120px;">
                <%= wicked_pdf_image_tag asset_url('logo.png'), class: "logo", alt: "Logo" %>
            </td>

            <!-- Centered Header Text -->
            <td class="header-text" style="text-align: center; flex-grow: 1;">
                <h1>Shri Guru Chanakya Souharda Sahakari Sangha Ltd. </h1>
                <h2>ಶ್ರೀ ಗುರು ಚಾಣಕ್ಯ ಸೌಹಾರ್ದ ಸಹಕಾರಿ ಸಂಘ ನಿಯಮಿತ</h2>
                <p><%= Current.branch.english_address %></p>
                <p>Phone: <%= Current.branch.phone_no %></p>
                <p>(R. NO. <%= Current.branch.r_no %>)</p>
                <h3>APPLICATION FOR "A"/ "B" CLASS MEMBERSHIP</h3>
                <p>"ಎ" "ಬಿ" ತರಗತಿಯ ಸದಸ್ಯತ್ವಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಅರ್ಜಿ</p>
            </td>

            <!-- Right-aligned Photo Box -->
            <td style="width: 100px; text-align: center;">
                <div class="photo-box">
                    <% if @member.profile_picture.attached? %>
                        <%
                          image_data = @member.profile_picture.download
                          base64_image = Base64.strict_encode64(image_data)
                          content_type = @member.profile_picture.content_type
                        %>
                        <img src="data:<%= content_type %>;base64,<%= base64_image %>" style="max-width: 150px; max-height: 170px; object-fit: cover;" />
                    <% else %>
                        <p>Paste Photo</p>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <div class="separator"></div>
 
    <div class="table-layout">
      <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell number">1.</div>
        <div class="table-cell labels">
          <span class="label-text">ಅರ್ಜಿದಾರನ ಹೆಸರು:</span>
          <span class="label-text">Name of the Applicant:</span>
          <span class="label-text">(IN CAPITAL LETTER)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell value"><%= @member.name.camelize %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell number">2.</div>
        <div class="table-cell labels">
          <span class="label-text"><%= @member.father_or_husband == "Father" ?  "ತಂದೆಯ" : "ಗಂಡನ" %> ಹೆಸರು:</span>
          <span class="label-text"><%= @member.father_or_husband %>'s Name:</span>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell value"><%= @member.father_or_husband_name.camelize %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell number">3.</div>
        <div class="table-cell labels">
          <span class="label-text">ಮೊಬೈಲ್ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆ:</span>
          <span class="label-text">Mobile No.:</span>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell value"><%= @member.mobile_number %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    
    <table class="table table-bordered zero-margin" style="width:100%;">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th class="number">4.</th>
      <th class="left-align">ಆಧಾರ್ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆ <br> Aadhaar No. <br> <div style="margin-top: 15px;"> <%= @member.aadhaar_number %></div> </th>
      <th>ಗುರುತು ಚೀಟಿ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆ <br> Voter ID No <br><div style="margin-top: 15px; "><%= @member.voter_id %></div> </th>
      <th>ಪಾನ್ ಕಾರ್ಡ್ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆ <br> Pan card No <br><div style="margin-top: 15px;  "><%= @member.pan_card %></div> </th>
      <th>ಡ್ರೈವಿಂಗ್ ಲೈಸೆನ್ಸ್ ನಂ <br> D.L.No <br><div style="margin-top: 15px;  "><%= @member.driving_license %></div> </th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
</table>
    <div class="separator no-margin"></div>
    <table class="table table-bordered zero-margin">
    <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" class="number">5.</th>
        <td rowspan="2" style="width: 10%; vertical-align: top" class="left-align">
                        ವಯಸ್ಸು <br>Age: <br /><div style="margin-top: 15px; font-weight: bold;"> <%= @member.age %></div>
        </td>
        <td style="width: 85%; padding-left: 10px"  class="with-border left-align">
             <div class="table-row no-border">
                <div class="table-cell number">6.</div>
                  <div class="table-cell labels">
                     <span class="label-text">  ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಹತೆ <br /> Educational qualification</span>
         
                  </div>
                  <div class="table-cell value"><%=@member.education.camelize %></div>
             </div>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="width: 50%; padding-left: 10px"  class="left-align">
             <div class="table-row no-border">
                <div class="table-cell number">7.</div>
                  <div class="table-cell labels">
                     <span class="label-text">  ಉದ್ಯೋಗ <br /> Occupation</span>
         
                  </div>
                  <div class="table-cell value"><%=@member.occupation.camelize %></div>
             </div>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
     <div class="separator no-margin"></div>
    
    
    <table class="table table-bordered zero-margin left-align small-padding">
    <tr>
        <th rowspan="5" class="number">8. </th>
        <td colspan="2"> ಖಾಯಂ ವಿಳಾಸ <br> Permanent Address </td>
        <td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 10px"> ಪ್ರಸಕ್ತ ವಿಳಾಸ <br> Present Address: </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class='no-border'>H. NO/Building Name:</td>
        <td> <%= @member.address_a_building %></td>
        <td class='no-border' style="padding-left: 10px">H. NO/Building Name:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_b_building %> </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        
        <td class='no-border'>Place, Village & Post:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_a_village %> </td>
        <td class='no-border' style="padding-left: 10px">Place, Village & Post:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_b_village %> </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class='no-border'>Taluk/District:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_a_district %> </td>
        <td class='no-border' style="padding-left: 10px">Taluk/District:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_b_district %> </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class='no-border'>Pincode:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_a_pincode %> </td>
        <td class='no-border' style="padding-left: 10px">Pincode:</td>
        <td>  <%= @member.address_b_pincode %> </td>
    </tr>
</table>
    <div class="separator no-margin"></div>

<table class="table table-bordered text-center">
    <tr>
        <td> 9. ಧರ್ಮ / Religion: </td>
        <td> 9ಎ. &nbsp; ಪ. ಜಾತಿ/ಪ. ಪಂಗಡ <br /> SC/ST </td>
        <td> 9ಬಿ. ಇತರ </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td> <%=@member.religion.camelize %></td>
        <td> <%=@member.caste_category == "1"  ? "Yes": "No" %> </td>
        <td><%=@member.religion_other == "1" ? "Yes": "No" %></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<div class="separator no-margin"></div>
<table class="table table-bordered  left-align">
    <tr>
        <td  style="width: 392px"> 10. ಪಾಲುಗಳ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆ <div style="padding-left: 25px">Number of shares Required </div> </td>
        <td style="width:100px; padding-left: 10px"><%=@membership.number_of_shares %></td>
        <td style="width: 374px; padding-left: 10px"  class="left-align"> 10ಎ. ಮೊಬಲಗು  <div style="padding-left: 50px">Amount: </div> </td>
        <td style="min-width:100px; padding-left: 10px"><%=@membership.amount %></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<div class="separator no-margin"></div>
<table class="table table-bordered">
    <tr>
        <th rowspan="5" class="number">11. </th>
        <td class="left-align" colspan=2>
            ವಾರಿಸುದಾರನ ಹೆಸರು ಮತ್ತು ವಿಳಾಸ ಹಾಗೂ ಅರ್ಜಿದಾರರೊಂದಿಗಿನ ಸಂಬಂಧ
        </td>
     </tr>
     <tr>
         <td class="left-align no-border">
            Name of the Nominee & Address:
         </td>
         <td><%=@membership.nominee_name.camelize %> <%=@membership.nominee_address %></td>
     </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="left-align no-border">
            And Relationship with Applicant:<br> 
            with Mobile No:
        </td>
        <td><%=@membership.nominee_relationship.camelize %> <br /> <%=@membership.nominee_phone.camelize %></td>
    </tr>
</table>

    
    <div class="page-break"></div>
    <p>ಮೇಲೆ ತಿಳಿಸಿದ ಎಲ್ಲಾ ವಿಷಯಗಳು ಸತ್ಯ ಎಂದು ದೃಢೀಕರಿಸುತ್ತೇನೆ. ನಾನು ಸಹಕಾರಿಯ ಈಗ ಇರುವ ಮತ್ತು  ಇನ್ನು ಮುಂದಕ್ಕೆ ಆಗಿಂದಾಗ್ಗೆ ಜಾರಿಗೆ ತರುವ ಎಲ್ಲಾ ಕಾನೂನು ಕಾಯ್ದೆ ಹಾಗೂ ಉಪನಿಬಂಧನೆಗಳಿಗೆ ಬದ್ಧನಾಗಿರುತ್ತೇನೆ.</p>                                
      <p>I certify that the above information are correct to the best of my knowldge. I will abide by the existing rules of the sahakari and also rules which may come into force in future from time to time. </p>                     
                    
    <div class="footer">
    
    <div class="left" style="width: 400px;">
        <p>ಸ್ಥಳ: <br /> Place:   <%= @membership.place %></p>
        <p>ದಿನಾಂಕ : <br /> Date: <%= format_date(@membership.signed_date) %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="right" style="width: 230px;">
        <br />
        <br />
        <p class="align-center"> ಅರ್ಜಿದಾರನ ಸಹಿ <br> Signature of the Applicant</p>
    </div>
</div>
 <div class="clearfix"></div>        
                                
 <div class="box">
        <p>ಅರ್ಜಿದಾರನ ಮಾದರಿ ಸಹಿ<br>Specimen Signature of the Applicant:</p>
        <div class="signatures">
            <table class="table" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px">
              <tr>
                <td> 1 </td>
                <td> 2 </td>
                <td> 3 </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Office Note Section -->
    <br />
    <div class="office-note">
        <p>ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಕಛೇರಿಯ ಟಿಪ್ಪಣಿ</p>
        <p style="font-size: 130%">OFFICE NOTE</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Information Table -->
    <table class="table" style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: left; width: 390px;">ಸದಸ್ಯತ್ವ ಅಂಗೀಕರಿಸಿದ ನಿರ್ಣಯ ನಂಬ್ರ<br>Approved Resolution No: <br />  <%=@membership.resolution_no %></td>
            <td>ದಿನಾಂಕ :<br>Date : <br />  
                <span style="display: inline-block; border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; min-width: 140px;">
                  &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <%= format_date(@membership.resolution_date) %> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
                </span>  </td>
            <td style="text-align: right">ಸದಸ್ಯ ನಂಬ್ರ<br>Member No. <br />  <%=@member.member_no %></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <br />
    <div class="separator no-margin"></div>
 
<div class="footer">
    <div class="left" style="width: 400px;">
        <p>ಸ್ಥಳ: <br /> Place:  <%= @membership.md_sign_place %></p>
        <p>ದಿನಾಂಕ : <br /> Date:  <%= format_date(@membership.md_signed_date) %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="right" style="width: 400px;  text-align: right;">
        <br />
        <br />
        <p>ಮುಖ್ಯ ಕಾರ್ಯನಿರ್ವಾಹಕ ಅಧಿಕಾರಿ<br> Chief Executive Officer/MD</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="clearfix"></div>       
   <div>
   <br />
   <br />
   ವಿಳಾಸ ದೃಢೀಕರಣಕ್ಕೆ ಪಡೆದುಕೊಂಡ ದಾಖಲೆಗಳು :   
     <ul>
     <li>1  ಮತದಾನದ ಗುರುತು ಚೀಟಿ</li>
     <li>2  ಪಡಿತರ ಚೀಟಿ</li>
     <li>3  ಡ್ರೈವಿಂಗ್ ಲೈಸನ್ಸ್</li>
     <li>4  ಪಾಸ್ ಪೋರ್ಟ್</li>
     <li>5  ಆಧಾರ್ ಕಾರ್ಡ್</li>
</div>


</div>

 
</body>
</html>
